data.description: This home is even more beautiful in person - beginning with not one, but TWO covered porches. Enjoy the sweeping views of the gorgeous Hocking Hills backdrop, breathtaking at sunrise, sunset, and everything in between. The open layout is airy and perfect for entertaining. The quartz kitchen has solid-wood cabinets, large island, and SS appliances. The dining space overlooks the covered back porch and yard. Perfect for hosting holiday meals or gathering for game night. First floor primary suite with back porch access, 3 large upstairs bedrooms with a full bath and half bath, plus a landing, loft or play area. FULL finished basement, flat yard with firepit, storage, 2-car attached garage, concrete drive, plus brand NEW roof and furnace/HVAC. Move right in and enjoy country living!
